<h1>Forms</h1>

<h3><%= step %></h3>
<% form_url = Rails.application.config.app_http_protocol + '://' +
              Rails.application.config.app_host + '/fake_post.json' %>
<p>Add this form code under <code>#logo</code>
<pre>
&lt;form action="<%= form_url %>" method="post"&gt;
  &lt;input name="name" type="text" placeholder="What is your name?"&gt;
  &lt;input name="answer[spelling]" type="text" placeholder="How do you spell dog?"&gt;
  &lt;input name="answer[maths]" type="text" placeholder="What is 1+2?"&gt;
  &lt;input type="submit" value="Submit"&gt;
&lt;/form&gt;
</pre>
<p>Test the form. You should see parameters. Press your back button.</p>
<p>Delete the form HTML.</p>

